description: Foundry: Sorkin Type Co Denk One is a medium contrast display sans serif. It was inspired by a hand painted German sign. It has been carefully adjusted to the restrictions of the screen. Despite having display characteristics, Denk One can be used in a wide range of sizes. Source files are available from Google Code. To contribute to the project contact Eben Sorkin.
